data.eml:eml: Alaskan Heteroptera (Hemiptera): new records, associated data, and deletions

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Scudder, G. G. E., Sikes, D. S. (2014): Alaskan Heteroptera (Hemiptera): new records, associated data, and deletions. Zootaxa 3852 (3): 373-381, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3852.3.6
